Name: UltraCommit
AboutMe:
I was born in Israel, finished high school there and served as a little unexperienced boy in the first eleven years, working for free.

I got my first computer at the age of 14, I still remember writing pages of wrong code and learning Basic off books...

I have been a professional software destroyer since 1996: I was paid for avoiding to use certain software.

I moved to London in 2001, working for different companies that, one by one, failed, due perhaps to my presence. I have been working as an indipendent contractor (very indipendent) for the last 6 years and 17 months.
